From aac4bf64943f294e100697553f16b17c5a51f101 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "vivy@aosp-builder" <vivy@aosp-builder>
Date: Sun, 14 Jun 2026 19:05:49 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 3/5] infiniti: add camera.oemlayer.v2 (OEM HAL) +
 libalogencrypt to proprietary-files

The makefile regen rebuilt Android.bp/infiniti-vendor.mk from
proprietary-files.txt, which silently dropped the hand-added
camera.oemlayer.v2 (the OEM camera HAL) + libalogencrypt modules
-> no camera HAL shipped. List them here so regen keeps them.
camera.oemlayer.v2.so exports HMI + OemLayer::process_capture_request.
---
 proprietary-files.txt | 3 +++
 1 file changed, 3 insertions(+)

diff --git a/proprietary-files.txt b/proprietary-files.txt
index 68f2d4e..bcd1552 100644
--- a/proprietary-files.txt
+++ b/proprietary-files.txt
@@ -952,6 +952,9 @@ odm/lib64/camera.oemlayer.adapter.so
 odm/lib64/camera.oemlayer.healthmonitor.so
 odm/lib64/camera.oemlayer.logger.so
 odm/lib64/camera.oemlayer.uilayer.so
+odm/lib64/hw/camera.oemlayer.v2.so
+odm/lib/libalogencrypt.so
+odm/lib64/libalogencrypt.so
 odm/lib64/com.oplus.mcx.linearmapper.so
 odm/lib64/com.oplus.node.preview.v2.so
 odm/lib64/lib2DSlender.so
